* **Dynamic sizing:** Map ke size automatically badh jaata hai jitne pairs add karenge.
* **Any datatype ke keys:**  Map me koi bhi datatype ke keys use kiya ja sakta hai.
* **Efficient lookup:** Map me key-value pair ko search karna bahut fast hai.

